message.body: Hi Scharx! Sorry for the delayed reply - are you still around tomorrow? Brunch maybe? I was gonna say let's hang out in a park but the rain...
Brunch sounds good. Maybe 10:30? Where r u guys staying? Do u have a car? Do u have a place you want to go or I can make some suggestions.
I started to txt you yesterday and got distracted and then forgot. Hope you had fun last night. Sweet maple sutter and pierce 10:30. Cute little neighborhood place. Hope that works
It maybe pushing it for Harrison bc he usually naps at 12. But we can try:).
Ok! We'll shoot for 1030 then. See you soon!
